Mission Orders

The indigenous creatures of Tuwangi Mire are hindering exploration efforts.

Eliminate the {@LinkCreature:5#14#muddy sporewalkers}, {@LinkCreature:5#15#hungry cullars}, and {@LinkCreature:5#16#tentacullars}.

Report to Zandra in Lumbertown when mission is complete.
